Twilight Vamps(2010) is a low budget erotic-horror film starring Brandin Rackley, Christine Nguyen and Beverly Lynne. It is not a rip off of the Twilight saga. It feels more like a Hammer Horror film or a 1970's grindhouse movie. The film has some silly humor such as a guy armed with a bottle of holy water labeled "Land O' Lourdes". There's serious scenes such as a guy finding out his wife is cheating on him. There's scary scenes where women turn into vampires and bite people! The real draw in the movie is the nudity and the soft core sex scenes. The CGI is decent for a B movie. It looks like something from a Playstation 3 game.  This is a solid effort from director "Nicolas Medina".
